metadata.name: RACECARS AFTER DARK
metadata.description:
[Tommaso Bertotti](https://www.tobephoto.com), 2022
PNG 8bit, 5760px × 3000px

There are racing liveries that will live forever: the orange Jäegermeister is for sure one of those.  
This picture was taken during the party organized by Rennmeister in Berlin, in occasion of the 50th anniversary from the first Stag's race. 

*Owner of this NFT benefits of the associated picture for personal purpose only. Copyright remains to the Author.*
